Fellow, Institute of Chartered Accountants of Ontario, London, Ontario. Director since April 2007
Criticism[edit]
In 2009 executives of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board took a 31.4% cut in their bonuses after questions were raised about the level of compensation at the crown corporation.[22]
