Canada Pension Plan Investment Board to Acquire an Approximate 48 Percent Stake in GlobalLogic Inc. from Apax Funds | Business Wire


























































Canada Pension Plan Investment Board to Acquire an Approximate 48 
      Percent Stake in GlobalLogic Inc. from Apax Funds












